  "id": "RAW_07c33423",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-7）：Kimi-K2-Thinking 开源，MoE 架构 + 256k 上下文，解锁复杂任务深度推理",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500229&idx=1&sn=e023dc9f9490670718c944b049d41c78",
  "date": "2025-11-07 09:49:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Kimi-K2-Thinking</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"432\" data-imgfileid=\"100016564\" data-ratio=\"0.37407407407407406\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=229362af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzel3Oj0eIsZNbjVXxVX3ZIDr40WUPROiatibqke9eeX8SGY5KqgT4ePiaHwapEWdQH5eZ1PuTW74Uibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Kimi-K2-Thinking 是 moonshot AI 推出的开源思考型大模型，专为复杂多步任务打造，兼具深度推理与动态工具调用能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Kimi-K2-Thinking 采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">混合专家（MoE）架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;256k 超长上下文窗口</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">端到端训练</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">实现思维链推理与函数调用的深度交织，支持连续 200-300 次稳定工具调用，同时借助原生 INT4 量化优化实现 2 倍推理加速。该模型在 HLE、BrowseComp 等多个基准测试中创下优异成绩，能有效提升复杂任务的执行效率与成功率，适用于科研、编码、智能搜索等各类需要深度推理的场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/kimi-k2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/kimi-k2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：RLinf</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"632\" data-imgfileid=\"100016565\" data-ratio=\"0.5462962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1319d4fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzel3Oj0eIsZNbjVXxVX3ZIccGVibjrcX5OFjmdRCBBg9hYsPSpNhUmnmehxI7qw3p3EHQDkJgqhdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★RLinf 是一套灵活可扩展的开源强化学习基础设施，专为基础模型（LLMs、VLMs、VLAs 等）的后训练打造。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">基于 RLinf 这一首个面向具身智能的大规模强化学习系统，清华、北大、CMU 等机构联合推出面向流匹配 VLA 的在线强化学习微调框架 πRL，提出&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Flow-Noise</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Flow-SDE</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;两种微调方案。该框架在 LIBERO 公开测试平台取得平均 97.6%（π0）和 98.3%（π0.5）的优异成绩，且在 4352 种抓取 - 放置任务组合的大规模训练中，成功率涨幅超 40% 并最终突破 80%，充分验证了方案有效性与大规模任务适配能力，目前全部代码、模型及文档示例已完全开源。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rlinf\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rlinf</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：AgentDebug</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"616\" data-imgfileid=\"100016566\" data-ratio=\"0.5314814814814814\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe62971c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzel3Oj0eIsZNbjVXxVX3ZIS8U8nNL9ycQVHJHHaczxMcFcfrq7fRicwM4BCSCWT0wcibhXbksA1RWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AgentDebug是一个用于理解、检测和恢复智能体失败的框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">集成规划、记忆、反思和工具使用模块</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，帮助大语言模型（LLM）智能体解决复杂的多步任务。然而，这些复杂系统容易出现级联失败，即单个根本原因错误会在后续决策中传播，最终导致任务失败。AgentDebug通过提供一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">系统化的失败轨迹数据集和智能调试系统</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，帮助智能体隔离根本原因错误并提供有针对性的纠正反馈，从而提高智能体的可靠性和任务成功率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agentdebug\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agentdebug</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：DeepOCR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"336\" data-imgfileid=\"100016563\" data-ratio=\"0.29074074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=666fe970&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzel3Oj0eIsZNbjVXxVX3ZIlib4hE9icPXEHaYzXNc59fkkUBLmJjwx2RkV0jPDuUVdx04vhA9GbBnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepOCR</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">通过视觉-文本令牌压缩探索上下文光学压缩，使用约250个视觉令牌实现了具有竞争力的OCR性能</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该项目</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">是基于VILA代码库的Deepseek-OCR模型的复现版本。DeepOCR提供了完整的训练管道、评估脚本和预训练检查点，便于立即使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepocr\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepocr</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Mem-alpha</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"358\" data-imgfileid=\"100016568\" data-ratio=\"0.3111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf69c559&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzel3Oj0eIsZNbjVXxVX3ZI48ftF6CSB885lvoWjJXLrGiaukg1ibIoQVicspOuf1gKc82xMib39OVmQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Mem-α 是一个通过增强学习来训练代理有效管理复杂记忆系统的框架。该项目旨在解决大语言模型（LLM）代理因上下文窗口限制而无法长期理解信息的问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Mem-α 通过交互和反馈优化记忆构建，具备核心、情节和语义记忆组件，能够在训练30k个token的基础上推广到400k+个token，显著提升现有记忆增强代理的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mem-alpha\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mem-alpha</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：UI-Genie</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"386\" data-imgfileid=\"100016569\" data-ratio=\"0.33425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=99b83ae5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzel3Oj0eIsZNbjVXxVX3ZIXiaaLyphUU7F9LAc9961H00Q0m5Uwk9xGsgcfafhMZWib5Vt8EZibxQHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UI-Genie是一个自我改进的框架，旨在通过迭代的Agent-奖励模型共同进化来增强基于MLLM的GUI智能体。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目无需人工标注，通过合成轨迹生成和奖励引导的探索，生成高质量的数据集，并在多个基准上实现了最先进的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ui-genie3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ui-genie3</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总介绍了包括 Moonshot AI 的 Kimi-K2-Thinking 大模型在内的多个前沿开源 AI 模型与框架，涵盖大模型推理、强化学习基础设施、Agent 调试与记忆管理、OCR 等领域，旨在提升复杂任务处理能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总介绍了包括 Moonshot AI 的 Kimi-K2-Thinking 大模型在内的多个前沿开源 AI 模型与框架，涵盖大模型推理、强化学习基础设施、Agent 调试与记忆管理、OCR 等领域，旨在提升复杂任务处理能力。",
  "summary": "该文章以“今日开源”的形式，集中介绍了六个在人工智能领域具有创新性和实用价值的开源项目。重点突出了由 Moonshot AI 推出的 Kimi-K2-Thinking 大模型，该模型采用混合专家（MoE）架构和 256k 超长上下文窗口，专为复杂多步任务设计，具备深度推理和动态工具调用能力，并通过原生 INT4 量化实现推理加速。此外，文章还介绍了清华、北大、CMU 等机构联合开发的强化学习基础设施 RLinf，旨在为基础模型（如 LLMs、VLMs）的后训练提供灵活可扩展的支持，并在具身智能任务中取得优异成绩。其他项目包括用于理解、检测和恢复智能体失败的 AgentDebug 框架、Deepseek-OCR 的复现版本 DeepOCR、通过增强学习优化记忆管理的 Mem-alpha 框架，以及用于提升 MLLM-based GUI 智能体的 UI-Genie 自我改进框架。这些项目共同展示了当前 AI 技术在模型架构、智能体开发、多模态处理等方面的最新进展，为技术从业者提供了丰富的开源资源和前沿参考。",
